{"name":"Savant","type":"class","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-embossed-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a Savant, you gain the following Class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice: </strong>1d8 per Savant level</p><p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level: </strong>8 + your Constitution modifier</p><p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels: </strong>1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per Savant level after 1st</p><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor: </strong>Light armor</p><p><strong>Weapons: </strong>Simple weapons, shortswords</p><p><strong>Tools: </strong>One set of artisan's tools of your choice</p><p><strong>Saving Throws: </strong>Intelligence, Wisdom</p><p><strong>Skills: </strong>Choose two from Arcana, History, Insight, Investigation, Medicine, Nature, Persuasion, or Religion</p><h3>Equipment</h3><p>As a Savant, you start with the following equipment, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p><ul><li><p><em>(a)</em> a simple weapon of your choice or <em>(b) </em>a shortsword.</p></li><li><p><em>(a)</em> a light crossbow and 20 bolts or <em>(b)</em> two daggers.</p></li><li><p>one set of artisan's tools of your choice.</p></li><li><p>leather armor, and a scholar's pack.</p></li></ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LaserLlama Homebrew","identifier":"savant","levels":1,"hitDice":"d8","hitDiceUsed":0,"advancement":[{"type":"HitPoints","configuration":{},"value":{},"title":"Hit Points","icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/svg/hit-points.svg","_id":"k33gTdEMyRY5lOrL"},{"type":"ScaleValue","configuration":{"identifier":"","type":"number","distance":{"units":""},"scale":{"5":{"value":2},"17":{"value":3}}},"value":{},"title":"Accelerated Reflexes Reactions","icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/svg/scale-value.svg","_id":"E5c7gtanZxVaM4FR"},{"type":"ScaleValue","configuration":{"identifier":"","type":"dice","distance":{"units":""},"scale":{"2":{"number":1,"faces":6},"5":{"number":1,"faces":8},"10":{"number":1,"faces":10},"15