{"name":"Undisputed Genius","type":"feat","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-open-purple.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You realize your true genius potential. Your Intelligence score increases by 4, up to a maximum of 24. Also, when you roll an Intellect Die and roll lower than your Intelligence modifier, you can replace the roll with your Intelligence modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LaserLlama Homebrew","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Savant 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"label":"Undisputed Genius","icon":"icons/sundries/books/book-open-purple.webp","origin":"Item.bNI8kAK0Ha1zJEMs","duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"disabled":false,"_id":"sTCat7grvFENrcXE","changes":[{"key":"system.abilities.int.value","mode":2,"value":"4","priority":null}],"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{}}],"flags":{"rsr5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFooter":{"value":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.H32cDWrjXX2uWfaM"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1681368396031,"modifiedTime":1681439629786,"lastModifiedBy":"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn":3},"_id":"TORxkiCkHodWBsix"}
{"name":"Quick Study","type":"feat","img":"icons/tools/scribal/lens-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You are able to gain a working knowledge of new concepts exceptionally fast. You gain proficiency with one skill, tool, or weapon, or learn to speak one language of your choice.</p><p>Over the course of 1 hour, which can be during a short or long rest, you can replace this proficiency or language with another proficiency or language of your choice, so long as you have an example to learn from. Examples include a willing teacher, a book in another language, or a tool set manual.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LaserLlama","activation":{"type":"hour","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Savant 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"rsr5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFooter":{"value":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cuOE4dWIA3IfC7fU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1681368396031,"modifiedTime":1681439628278,"lastModifiedBy":"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn":3},"_id":"TpVXmKMQftCpffrs"}
{"name":"Linguistics","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-handshake.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You learn to speak, read, and write a number of languages equal to your Intelligence modifier.</p><p>Whenever you make a Charisma (Persuasion) check while speaking with a creature in its native tongue (other than Common) you can treat a roll of 9 or lower on the d20 as a 10.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LaserLlama Homebrew","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"rsr5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFooter":{"value":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.szqNqLGjnKG7wKLs"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1681380339280,"modifiedTime":1681451976027,"lastModifiedBy":"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn":3},"_id":"TqpwbP4EUlWAGJY4"}
{"name":"Field Doctor","type":"feat","img":"icons/tools/laboratory/mortar-empty-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You have learned to move across the battlefield unscathed. When you use your action to stabilize, restore hit points, or grant temporary hit points to another creature, you gain the benefits of the Dodge action until the start of your next turn.</p><p>Additionally, when you use a Combat Medic action on your turn, you can make a single weapon attack as a bonus action</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LaserLlama Homebrew","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Physician 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"rsr5e":{"quickDesc":{"value":true},"quickFooter":{"value":true}},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DPu9C5FuZiK7XHGg"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1681375138740,"modifiedTime":1681439888694,"lastModifiedBy":"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"tl7rQdo93TVsRvdn":3},"_id":"UjDX1ks9a9FkTeif"}
{"name":"Staff of the Headmaster","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-crescent-purple.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>(requires attunement by a savant)</em></p><p>This austere staff was once a symbol of the headmaster at an imperial academy. It can be wielded as a magic quarterstaff that grants a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with it. When holding it, you have a +2 bonus to any ability checks you make that use your Intelligence or Wisdom.</p><p>Moreover, you can use an action to plunge this staff into the ground, producing the effect of <em>private sanctum</em> within a 30-foot radius of that point. The area within the spell appears as a ornate study in addition to the normal effects of the spell.</p><p>Once you use the staff to cast <em>private sanctum</em> in this way, it cannot do so again until the following dawn.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LaserLlama Homebrew","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6 + @mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":"1d8 + @mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null},"hp":{"value":null,"max":null,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"quarterstaff","properties":{"ada":false,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"hvy":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"mgc":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"sil":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false},"proficient":true},"effects"